## Prophesee portal auth
PROPHESSEE_SUPPORT_BRAND_URL=https://support.prophesee.ai
PROPHESSEE_SUPPORT_LOGIN_PAGE="https://support.prophesee.ai/accounts/signin?_sh=false&client_portal=true&servicename=ZohoSupport"
